{"tid":1894831,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國權鬥正式啟動！武漢地方政府違反北京指令！","createTime":"2020-02-24T07:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T07:35:37.000Z","uid":222970,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c2303f40bd001186cff8a62c892734e4089db050","tid":1894831,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:21:34.000Z","msg":"【武漢宣布：放開離漢通道的通告無效】<br />\n2020-02-24 15:10<br />\n<br />\n武漢市新冠肺炎疫情防控指揮部發布的《關於加強進出武漢市車輛和人員管理的通告》（第17號），系市指揮部下設的交通防控組未經指揮部研究和主要領導同志同意發布的，現宣布該通告無效。對此，我們對相關人員進行了嚴肅的批評處理。武漢市堅決貫徹習近平總書記關於&ldquo;外防輸出&rdquo;的重要指示精神，牢固樹立全國一盤棋的思想，嚴格離漢通道管理，嚴格人員管控，嚴防疫情向外輸出。（武漢發布）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>武漢獨立，唯一出路！<br />\n光復武漢，時代革命！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"82a732af26f4ebb5dcdfd8c965417e2b9694bb74","tid":1894831,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:22:43.000Z","msg":"即係繼續封城 ?"},{"pid":"2a4f003776f250f31b5c0beaaaeb4e1568fb0b5c","tid":1894831,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82a732af26f4ebb5dcdfd8c965417e2b9694bb74","tid":1894831,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:22:43.000Z","msg":"即係繼續封城 ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7219365942055b7222226f094027d0606dcdaae3","tid":1894831,"uid":306681,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:25:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7311f4fbbd300cc46bfedcab860342d0efe2369","tid":1894831,"uid":128178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:25:31.000Z","msg":"全國一盤棋都講得出口<br />\n當人民棋子"},{"pid":"a7606286f5d12bbd7ca1dd50b243464d72192368","tid":1894831,"uid":2257